Anyway, for those who are too poor or cheap to afford the ten bucks the movie costs, here's what a nuclear explosion in space looks like, sequentially (as seen in the best shot): <br>
1) A flash of light<br>
2) a sphere of glowing light<br>
3) a roiled cloud within the sphere (looks like the Crab Nebula)<br>
